                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290611-378-off1963 t18290611-378-cd1964"></join>, at St. Anne, 2 pins, value 4s.; 1 brooch, value 4s.; 3 coats, value 6l.; 4 pairs of trousers, value 2l.; 1 handkerchief, value 4s.; 1 box, value 5s.; 1 waistcoat, value 12s.; 1 shirt, value 5s.; 1 pocket-book, value 1s.; 5 sovereigns, and 1 half-sovereign, the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18290611-378-victim2619" type="victimName">
