                     <interp inst="t18290611-378-person2621" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . This is Mr. Hunt's coat - I made it for him some time before Christmas.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. If you will send to Mr. Ward, the pawnbroker, he will prove that I bought a duplicate, gave 1s. 6d. for it, and paid 2s. for the interest; I had a green coat which I wore, but this coat was too large for me, and I pawned it for 25s. - I never ran away.</p>
